  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to rise to the challenge and become the hero you were born to be?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625330/extras/0a8113133197a173d0c6627da707815e.poster.avif?t=1771002696\" width=780 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625330/extras/0a8113133197a173d0c6627da707815e.webm?t=1771002696\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625330/extras/0a8113133197a173d0c6627da707815e.mp4?t=1771002696\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625330/extras/ab1bc89c432df24d48454318e36820a3.poster.avif?t=1771002696\" width=591 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625330/extras/ab1bc89c432df24d48454318e36820a3.webm?t=1771002696\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625330/extras/2ce6eb2791d8dfdce1fd846c25825429.poster.avif?t=1771002696\" width=780 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625330/extras/2ce6eb2791d8dfdce1fd846c25825429.webm?t=1771002696\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625330/extras/2ce6eb2791d8dfdce1fd846c25825429.mp4?t=1771002696\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Embark on a breathtaking journey unlike any other in \"UpWorld - Multiplayer,\" a parkour adventure that will challenge your skills, your heart, and your sense of wonder. Reach for the skies as you scale towering cliffs, navigate treacherous chasms, and defy gravity in your quest to reach the mythical Upworld.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625330/extras/5c77d617f6653ababaef5fc7a60c6e14.poster.avif?t=1771002696\" width=780 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625330/extras/5c77d617f6653ababaef5fc7a60c6e14.webm?t=1771002696\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625330/extras/5c77d617f6653ababaef5fc7a60c6e14.mp4?t=1771002696\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are the chosen one, entrusted with the sacred \"Celestial Relic\" - a mission that will take you through a world teeming with wonder and enchantment. Encounter a cast of mystical creatures and characters who will aid you on your journey, from wise guardians to imprisoned angels, all of whom have destinies entwined with yours. As you ascend, you won't just face challenges; you'll forge deep connections. You will also challenged by some Puzzles.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625330/extras/931f2ef763e4fed2f660b737bec85a29.poster.avif?t=1771002696\" width=780 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625330/extras/931f2ef763e4fed2f660b737bec85a29.webm?t=1771002696\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625330/extras/931f2ef763e4fed2f660b737bec85a29.mp4?t=1771002696\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover hidden powers and abilities as you progress, enhancing your parkour skills and empowering you to overcome even the most daunting obstacles. otherworldly landscapes will leave you in awe, from lush, magical forests to towering, crystalline spires. Your adventure begins now in \"UpWorld - Multiplayer,\" where the fate of a world rests on your shoulders.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625330/extras/b1ef701ac469844c6cce522c11f6ae84.poster.avif?t=1771002696\" width=720 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625330/extras/b1ef701ac469844c6cce522c11f6ae84.webm?t=1771002696\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2625330/extras/b1ef701ac469844c6cce522c11f6ae84.mp4?t=1771002696\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to rise to the challenge and become the hero you were born to be?</p>",
